from Temple University.

39
00:05:58,525 --> 00:06:00,527
He's a cornerback.

40
00:06:00,611 --> 00:06:04,364
This kid is 6'1 ", 210 pounds.

41
00:06:04,448 --> 00:06:08,619
He runs a 40 in 4.3 seconds.
