42
00:06:08,702 --> 00:06:11,705
Do you like football?

43
00:06:11,788 --> 00:06:13,790
Not really.

44
00:06:25,052 --> 00:06:28,764
- I'm David Dunn.
- Kelly.

45
00:06:28,847 --> 00:06:31,600
- Hi.
- Hi, nice to meet you.

46
00:06:31,683 --> 00:06:33,685
Nice-Nice to meet you.

47
00:06:41,276 --> 00:06:43,862
How long are you gonna be
in Philadelphia?

48
