61
00:09:19,017 --> 00:09:20,936
<i>We are not sure at this time, uh...</i>

62
00:09:21,019 --> 00:09:23,522
<i>how rescue personnel will be able
to get on scene at all.</i>

63
00:09:23,605 --> 00:09:26,191
<i>If you'rejust tuning in,
Eastrail train number 177...</i>

64
00:09:26,275 --> 00:09:28,694
<i>has derailed
